<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Order Has Shipped</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f4f6f9;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background: #f4f6f9;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
            padding: 40px 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .body {
            padding: 36px 40px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .tracking-card {
            background: #f0faf6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 22px 26px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            border-left: 4px solid #11998e;
        }

        .tracking-card .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 6px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d9f0e8;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .tracking-card .row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .tracking-card .label {
            color: #666;
        }

        .tracking-card .value {
            color: #222;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fc;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <span class="icon">ðŸ“¦</span>
                <h1>Your Order is On Its Way!</h1>
                <p>Great news â€” your package has been shipped.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="body">
                <p class="greeting">Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,<br />Your order is on its way to you!</p>

                <div class="tracking-card">
                    <div class="row"><span class="label">Order Number</span><span class="value">#{{orderNumber}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row"><span class="label">Carrier</span><span class="value">{{carrier}}</span></div>
                    <div class="row"><span class="label">Tracking Number</span><span
                            class="value">{{trackingNumber}}</span></div>
                    {{#if estimatedDelivery}}
                    <div class="row"><span class="label">Estimated Delivery</span><span
                            class="value">{{estimatedDelivery}}</span></div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>

                <div class="cta">
                    <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="btn">Track My Package</a>
                </div>

                <p style="font-size:14px;color:#666;line-height:1.7;">
                    Please allow a few hours for the tracking information to update with the carrier.
                    If you have any issues with your delivery, contact our support team.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size:14px;color:#666;">Best regards,<br /><strong>The MarketX Team</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>You received this email because you placed an order on MarketX.</p>
                <p>&copy; {{year}} MarketX Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>